Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.98,PS1,NTP,0,0,0,,要上发条吗  不上发条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要上发条吗  不上发条吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:05.20,PS1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}要上发条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我从学校回来就看到这个放在门口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是寄给纯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯终于也和正常人一样开始对女孩子感兴趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给爸爸妈妈发短信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做工很精良啊  软软的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然穿着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发条？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一见面就伸手乱摸淑女的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时代竟然已经进步到了这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？  樱田纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个不美丽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是真红
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔷薇少女的第五人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(539,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而纯  你今后就是我真红的仆人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仆人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙到底被设定了些什么对话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  亲吻那只戒指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拔不下来……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要亲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给我沏红茶来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要用95℃以上温度的热水冲泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后加上热牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要做这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你  这样就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,温度太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶叶没泡开  香气也散逸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本不能叫红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久违
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,58万6920小时又37分没见了呢  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔷薇少女的第一人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(541,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,七位蔷薇少女都醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(601,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝游戏开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝游戏  又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯  快亲吻戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是挑衅在先哦  水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能放出人工精灵来就比较麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(702,656)}Meimei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嘛  人家害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再会吧  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  真红  刚才那是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔷薇少女人偶共有七位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(518,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是七姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是将原本独一无二的蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(882,656)}Rosa Mystica
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分成七个碎片制作出的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每人只是七分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须把七分之一的碎片恢复到一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们要互相争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了孕育父亲梦中的少女爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雏梅  别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不哭  所以你要快点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
