Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想你啊  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  这个人类是无害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是仆人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那她也是那个蔷薇什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蔷薇少女的第三人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(578,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翠星石…的说
