Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是聒噪啊  明天会修的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我的说  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你？  说起来真是奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然会单独出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你形影不离的双胞胎妹妹哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹…苍星石被扣作人质了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人质？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您叫我吗  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蔷薇少女第四人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(606,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该也是被某个人类上了发条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的说  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪  你的戒指呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要交给那种人类的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翠星石醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石被那个坏人类欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经缔结了契约的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明在这之前我们不管什么都是一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我告诉她不愿意这样的说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可苍星石她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不愿服从主人  你就不应该留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翠星石好伤心  就一个人逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人类还真舍得放翠星石离开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来那个人类没有注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将双胞胎人偶配成一对的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他迟早都会来抢夺翠星石的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯  吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拨弦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,656)\fs-2}Pizzicato
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于  终于被我找到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真红和翠星石根本不足为惧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来蔷薇圣母就能一次拿到两份了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:12:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(516,656)}Rosa Mystica
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(712,656)\fs-2}Lempicka
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下你一人之后  感觉真是既残缺又凄凉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们姐妹全都是不完整的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀你生气啦  不过不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是来做交易的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.92,0:12:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交易？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想拯救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想要找的东西在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在某个地方  门被打开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个香味是锡兰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错的茶叶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经在我的领域里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这个世界是在梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人的命令我来夺取你的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不要这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我打么？翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真让我高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们双胞胎一直形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今后也要一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又哭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看着你哭泣的脸庞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛就像看到了镜中的自己一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,曾令我如此厌恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蔷薇圣母
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,656)\fs-2}Rosa Mystica
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我成为你的一部分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不要这样  苍星…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水银灯  你！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了耶  拿到了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,苍星石的蔷薇圣母是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(643,656)}Rosa Mystica
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我  水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要呢  我等的就是这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒  竟然如此舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.78,0:16:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,力…力量从身体里面喷涌而出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是为了绝望而诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那便是爱丽丝游戏的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要埋伏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以趁别人进出的时候从大门进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好晚好晚！今天也好晚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏…小雏明明是是蔷薇少女第六个人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.37,0:17:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(709,656)\fs-2}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的时候  你要躲在箱子里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏很寂寞嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我玩嘛  小巴  和我玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}巴小姐  怎么了  很吵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴小巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  打不开？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不让你去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  吃饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有…有人在吗？哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小巴  小巴  小巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不要  小巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  这是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蔷薇少女第七人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(602,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪华绮晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第七人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第七人偶没有实体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还没能够成为爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要补完自己  成为至高的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要容器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要空的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果铃？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(621,656)\fs-2}Berrybell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少女大姐大  华丽降临了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蔷薇少女第二人偶  金丝雀了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(486,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人是小美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小美？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雏莓  你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  小雏已经回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雏被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然身体已经被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是小雏的蔷薇圣母就交给最喜欢的真红吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(536,656)\fs-2}Rosa Mystica
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快拿走  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在第七人找到这里之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是从以太中解放出的星芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有实体的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我拿到了  空无一物的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小纯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真红和翠星石她们从昨天到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  大家的晚饭我都做了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.84,0:21:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须去那个世界才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,连接不同的两处之物  那就是门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这后面是n之领域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要打开？或不打开？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打开门
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也给大家带来放松的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,BOOKS  TAKIWA出品  店内广播
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算开始了呢  小斋藤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提  请别叫我叫得那么亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.88,0:23:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么进入正题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今后也希望大家能够喜欢纸质书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,店长喜欢什么书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.01,0:23:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:24:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于怎样成为高帅富的指南书我应该都收齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗  没人说你恶心么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里  没有那么厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.91,0:24:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过从刚才我就很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你肩膀上的那个女孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回见
